Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 路上堵车了\N{\rEN}Sorry, there was traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌早班了\N{\rEN}I hate the morning shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吐得到处都是\N{\rEN}There was always vomit everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就像前几天在七子通公园厕所一样…\N{\rEN}Like the other day at Nanago Dori Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就在涩谷的幡谷\N{\rEN}...in Hatagaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太可怕了\N{\rEN}It was truly terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个昏迷很久的人\N{\rEN}There is someone who has been out for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了 十分可以打八分\N{\rEN}The horror level is 8 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在听我说话吗\N{\rEN}Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦了 桧山先生 反正没过多久还是会变脏\N{\rEN}No need to bother, Mr. Hiyarama. It'll get dirty again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEN}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEN}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是妈妈带你过来的吗\N{\rEN}Are you here with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事儿的\N{\rEN}Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,仗助\N{\rEN}Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈正在找你呢\N{\rEN}Mom is looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人啊\N{\rEN}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在到处找你呢\N{\rEN}Mom is looking for you everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说不要走得太远吗\N{\rEN}Didn't Mom say not to go too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我在公园里到处找你呢\N{\rEN}Mom is looking all over the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈\N{\rEN}I'm sorry Mom, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在弟弟也哭了\N{\rEN}Now he was crying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈\N{\rEN}I'm sorry mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在好了\N{\rEN}Now it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这要怎么用\N{\rEN}How does this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 欢迎光临\N{\rEN}Hello, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.98,0:25:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\rEN}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.03,0:25:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,犒劳一下你\N{\rEN}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.71,0:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 他打中了\N{\rEN}Yes! He hit the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.96,0:25:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 没错吧\N{\rEN}He's in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.72,0:25:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了没\N{\rEN}He's in! Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.84,0:25:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你干嘛\N{\rEN}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:26:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,打赌吗 这有什么好玩儿的\N{\rEN}Playing bets? Where's the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.23,0:26:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凯酱 退后\N{\rEN}Kat-chan! Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.43,0:26:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你要尊重别人支持的队伍或者是宗教什么的 来击个掌\N{\rEN}Always respect other people's sports teams or religions. High five!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.39,0:26:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回去吧\N{\rEN}Now go away. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.28,0:26:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们作弊了\N{\rEN}They cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.69,0:26:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把其他队里厉害的球手挖走了\N{\rEN}They steal great players from other teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.28,0:33:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEN}Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.57,0:33:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,绫 你来啦\N{\rEN}Aya! You come!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.53,0:33:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,百分之百的惊喜\N{\rEN}What a surprise! The rating is 10 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.04,0:33:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等 还剩最后一个地方了\N{\rEN}Wait a moment! This is the last place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.08,0:33:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就结束了\N{\rEN}I'm about to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.18,0:33:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你还是能很有效率地工作呀\N{\rEN}Turns out you can work fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.26,0:33:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女孩在等我呢 我要下班了\N{\rEN}There's a girl waiting for me. I'm done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.13,0:34:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEN}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 你的车能借我用一下吗\N{\rEN}Mr Hiyarama, may I borrow your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.81,0:34:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 我可不能错过今天晚上的机会\N{\rEN}I can't miss this opportunity tonight. Mr. Hiyarama, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.85,0:34:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEN}I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.19,0:34:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rEN}Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的前辈 桧山先生\N{\rEN}This is Mr. Hiyarama, my senior at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.79,0:34:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,认真勤勉 而且还很安静\N{\rEN}Hard worker, but very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.87,0:34:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可没有人这么说过我\N{\rEN}I don't even know what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.21,0:34:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这是绫\N{\rEN}Mr. Hiyarama, this is Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.84,0:34:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对的满分女孩\N{\rEN}Definitely a 10 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.88,0:34:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说了\N{\rEN}Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.64,0:35:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这个还能放吗\N{\rEN}Can this be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.42,0:35:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\rEN}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.86,0:35:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个声音\N{\rEN}I like the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.57,0:35:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rEN}Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.62,0:36:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,史密斯\N{\rEN}Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.37,0:36:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很常见的名字\N{\rEN}Very common name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.45,0:36:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\rEN}Pak Hiyarama,...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,…你真的喜欢这份工作吗\N{\rEN}...do you really like this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.79,0:36:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至有自己的设备和工具\N{\rEN}You have your own equipment and tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.21,0:36:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这种工作你为什么还要这么努力呢\N{\rEN}How can you work so hard at a job like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不必回答我\N{\rEN}You don't have to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.55,0:36:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇\N{\rEN}I'm just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.64,0:36:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人很奇怪\N{\rEN}This person is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.51,0:36:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,满分十分可以打九分\N{\rEN}The scale is oddly 9 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.36,0:36:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢盒式磁带的声音\N{\rEN}I like the sound of cassette recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.44,0:36:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 卡带的声音听起来很棒\N{\rEN}Yes! The cassette sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.70,0:36:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次听\N{\rEN}This is my first time listening to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.20,0:36:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次总是最好的\N{\rEN}The first time is always good!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.25,0:37:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿把我放下\N{\rEN}Drop me off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.97,0:37:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是在约会吗\N{\rEN}Aren't we on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.68,0:37:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧要加班\N{\rEN}I have an extra shift at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.18,0:37:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你来的话 我可以陪你一晚上\N{\rEN}If you come, I'll be with you all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.18,0:37:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没发工资呢\N{\rEN}I'm still waiting for my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.13,0:37:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这对我来说非常重要\N{\rEN}Mr. Hiyarama, this is very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,人没钱的话还谈什么恋爱啊\N{\rEN}People can't fall in love without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.56,0:37:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界到底怎么了\N{\rEN}What happened to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.14,0:37:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是现代吗\N{\rEN}Is this the modern era?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.57,0:38:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个值多少钱啊\N{\rEN}What is the price for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想知道吗\N{\rEN}Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.04,0:38:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇\N{\rEN}I'm just curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.33,0:38:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西又流行起来了 没准儿这些很值钱呢\N{\rEN}Analog is back in trend. All of this may be of great value.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.04,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的只是好奇而已 我知道下北有一个估价地地方\N{\rEN}I'm really just curious! I know a suitable place in Shimokita.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.84,0:38:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去\N{\rEN}I didn't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.72,0:38:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,都用不上三十分钟\N{\rEN}It only takes less than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.43,0:38:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就在这里的...\N{\rEN}It should be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.73,0:38:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里 看到了吧\N{\rEN}Here, that's the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.65,0:38:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,借过\N{\rEN}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.83,0:38:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 这个现在值多少\N{\rEN}Excuse me, how much is the selling price for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,卢·里德的磁带很少见啊\N{\rEN}This one is rare, it's Lou Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.09,0:39:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个的话值12000日元\N{\rEN}For this, 12 thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.46,0:39:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rEN}Very?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.21,0:39:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个值8000  - 真的吗\N{\rEN}- For this 8000.   - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.13,0:39:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这些磁带你是从哪儿弄到的\N{\rEN}Where did you get these tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.27,0:39:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的前辈的\N{\rEN}They belong to my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.31,0:39:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个得有4000日元\N{\rEN}This one is 4000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.39,0:39:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这盘差不多6000 你手里的这些值很多钱呢\N{\rEN}This one can be sold for 6000. You can make a lot of money from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.07,0:39:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这还只是估计\N{\rEN}This is my estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\rEN}My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.91,0:39:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 我们把这些都卖掉吧\N{\rEN}Extraordinary! Mr. Hiyarama, let's sell all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的我们都要 现在这个很流行\N{\rEN}We accept everything. Cassettes are trending.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是七八十年代的磁带\N{\rEN}Especially cassettes from the 70s and 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.99,0:39:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把你的收藏都卖了吧\N{\rEN}We have to sell it, your entire collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.21,0:39:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,光是这盘就值12000\N{\rEN}Twelve thousand just for this tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.25,0:39:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正是时候\N{\rEN}Now is the perfect time!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.71,0:39:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一个 就卖一个也行\N{\rEN}OK, just one. We'll just sell one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.14,0:39:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就可以去酒吧见绫了 今晚对我真的很重要\N{\rEN}Then I can go to the bar to meet Aya. This is a very important night for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.52,0:40:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很重要\N{\rEN}This is a very important night for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.40,0:40:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我错过这个机会...\N{\rEN}If I miss this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.69,0:40:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有钱还哪有什么爱情生活 是吧\N{\rEN}No love life if we're broke? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.28,0:40:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEN}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,恩人 我先走了\N{\rEN}You saved me! I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.04,0:41:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你最棒了 桧山先生\N{\rEN}You're the best, Mr. Hiyarama!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.83,0:41:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎下次光临\N{\rEN}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.96,0:54:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEN}Thank You!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.22,0:54:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\rEN}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.59,0:54:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我跟绫不会在一起了 大概只有两成的机会\N{\rEN}I don't think it's possible for me to be with Aya. Chances are 2 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.26,0:54:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不会放弃的放弃\N{\rEN}But that doesn't mean I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.99,0:54:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\rEN}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.95,0:54:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没结婚吧\N{\rEN}You're not married yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.79,0:54:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个年纪还一个人\N{\rEN}Alone at your age..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.25,0:54:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不会觉得孤独吗\N{\rEN}Don't you ever feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,高志\N{\rEN}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.63,0:55:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\rEN}It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.05,0:55:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,高志\N{\rEN}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经很久没见面了  - 高志\N{\rEN}- We haven't seen each other for a long time.  - Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.31,0:55:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\rEN}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.48,0:55:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找你呢\N{\rEN}I am looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.31,0:55:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗  - 是啊\N{\rEN}- Very?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.81,0:55:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这是我的好朋友寺酱\N{\rEN}Mr. Hiyarama, this is Dera-chan, my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.86,0:55:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 他很喜欢我的耳朵\N{\rEN}As you can see, he likes my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.15,0:55:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,每次见面都会握住\N{\rEN}Every time he meets me, he holds it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.07,0:55:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不管我到哪里 他总是能找到我\N{\rEN}He always finds me. 10 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.29,0:55:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢我的耳朵 ...\N{\rEN}Dera-chan likes my ears,...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.66,0:55:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要变成什么挂件了\N{\rEN}...and I'm just the accessory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.70,0:55:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 是吧\N{\rEN}- Yes. -  Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.86,0:56:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这个还给你\N{\rEN}I want to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.65,0:56:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\rEN}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.33,0:56:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我能再听一遍吗\N{\rEN}Can I listen to it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.37,0:57:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.96,0:57:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,贵司有跟你说什么吗\N{\rEN}Did Takashi tell you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.16,0:59:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\rEN}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.84,1:00:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是犒劳你的\N{\rEN}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.34,1:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.47,1:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,文库新书 每本100日元\N{\rEN}100 YEN FOR THE BOOKS
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.75,1:06:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,幸田文【日本女作家】应该更出名的\N{\rEN}Aya Koda should be more famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.04,1:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她的遣词很日常 但是依旧很特别\N{\rEN}He uses common word choices, but is still special.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 桧山先生\N{\rEN}Good evening, Mr. Hiyarama.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.49,1:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是老样子吗\N{\rEN}The usual message?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.99,1:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在读什么\N{\rEN}What are you reading now?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.79,1:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,幸田文的木\N{\rEN}Aya Koda "Pohon".
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.58,1:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,散文吗\N{\rEN}The essay?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.50,1:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你读过吗\N{\rEN}Have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.75,1:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有学识\N{\rEN}You're very educated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.88,1:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这么觉得\N{\rEN}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.59,1:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的土豆沙拉...\N{\rEN}Here's your potato salad...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.97,1:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有酒水...\N{\rEN}...and here's to a long day.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.06,1:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘 我们怎么都没有前菜\N{\rEN}Mom, we didn't get the appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.73,1:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 肯定有的\N{\rEN}I'm sure I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.35,1:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那也没有这么多\N{\rEN}We never got that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.06,1:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 我对大家可是一视同仁的\N{\rEN}That is not true. We're all equal here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.57,1:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可得去字典里查查这个词\N{\rEN}I had to look up the word "equality" in the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,女人可不喜欢多嘴的男人\N{\rEN}Women don't like talkative men.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.08,1:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这里一直有皱纹吗\N{\rEN}Have you always had wrinkles here?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.20,1:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 就一个 在那里\N{\rEN}No, the only one. There.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.84,1:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘 还有炸豆腐吗\N{\rEN}Mama, do you have fried tofu?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.13,1:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经卖光了  你要的话我一会儿去做\N{\rEN}No, it's finished. I'll make it later if you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.80,1:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他的妻子丢下他走了\N{\rEN}His wife left him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.22,1:08:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么还这么开心呢\N{\rEN}How could he be so cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.97,1:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是在说我吗\N{\rEN}Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.22,1:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEN}There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.47,1:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我的妻子离开我了 我还这么高兴\N{\rEN}How can you be cheerful when your wife left you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.36,1:08:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单啊 因为我终于可以没有负担地一个人生活了\N{\rEN}That is easy. Finally I can live alone again without burdens.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.23,1:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都会很开心的\N{\rEN}It makes all men happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.12,1:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能够摆脱挑挑拣拣的女人真是一种解脱\N{\rEN}It's a relief to be able to get rid of fussy women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.66,1:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还强撑着呢\N{\rEN}You pretend to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.24,1:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,过不了多久 你就要跟老板娘哭诉你有多孤独了\N{\rEN}Soon you will confide in Mama how lonely you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.71,1:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,左不过是些无聊的故事\N{\rEN}Just boring stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.34,1:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要再来一杯吗\N{\rEN}Want another drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.67,1:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请\N{\rEN}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.43,1:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么世界上没有能保持不变的事物呢\N{\rEN}Why can't everything stay the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.47,1:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘\N{\rEN}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.94,1:09:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们唱那首歌吧\N{\rEN}Sing us that song.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.73,1:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的最爱\N{\rEN}Our favorite.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.52,1:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那首啊\N{\rEN}Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.36,1:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但桧山先生才刚到\N{\rEN}But Mr. Hiyarama had just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.87,1:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我们难过呀\N{\rEN}Don't disappoint us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.03,1:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是呀\N{\rEN}Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.87,1:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEN}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.17,1:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你已经拿出吉他了...\N{\rEN}Since you've already got the guitar out... Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.63,1:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一首优美的歌曲\N{\rEN}This is a beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.55,1:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我到了一个叫\N{\rEN}I got to the place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.94,1:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,新奥尔良的地方\N{\rEN}in New Orleans
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.56,1:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到了一家叫旭日之屋\N{\rEN}to a place called a brothel
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.99,1:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,的妓院\N{\rEN}"House of the Rising Sun"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.33,1:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱的男人\N{\rEN}The man I love
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.89,1:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有回来\N{\rEN}he didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.26,1:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时我离开了\N{\rEN}That's when I left
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.81,1:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖国\N{\rEN}your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.32,1:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我上了火车\N{\rEN}I got on the train,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.58,1:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有回头...\N{\rEN}and in a matter of seconds...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.44,1:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两杯柠檬水\N{\rEN}And two lemonades!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你来啦 稍等一下\N{\rEN}You've arrived, just wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.37,1:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\rEN}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.75,1:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\rEN}Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.51,1:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪来的\N{\rEN}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.84,1:14:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经等你很久了\N{\rEN}I've been waiting for you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.72,1:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你家是哪扇门\N{\rEN}Which door is your house?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.65,1:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上还是楼下\N{\rEN}Upstairs or downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.36,1:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是Niko吗\N{\rEN}Niko?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.11,1:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你长这么大了\N{\rEN}You're big!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.40,1:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔...\N{\rEN}Uncle,...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.07,1:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,…你要上班吗\N{\rEN}...you're going to work?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.95,1:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以一起去吗\N{\rEN}can i come along
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.33,1:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该让我跟着的\N{\rEN}Uncle should let me come along.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.29,1:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人的话可不知道会做出什么事情\N{\rEN}I don't know what I would do if I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.65,1:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从那边上\N{\rEN}Enter from the next door.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.58,1:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要咖啡吗\N{\rEN}Would you like coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.16,1:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要\N{\rEN}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.25,1:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一样吗\N{\rEN}The same as me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.59,1:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEN}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.39,1:18:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.48,1:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要放进去吗  - 是的\N{\rEN}- Do you want to set it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.31,1:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEN}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.78,1:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是这边\N{\rEN}This side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.12,1:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 像这样吗  - 是的\N{\rEN}- Like this?  -  Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.12,1:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,磁带卷在这边\N{\rEN}The tape is on this side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.52,1:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是东京晴空塔吗\N{\rEN}What is Sky Tree tower?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.60,1:18:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Oh, benar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.58,1:19:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这就是盒式录音带\N{\rEN}So, this is a cassette?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.67,1:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是你那个年代的吗\N{\rEN}From ancient times?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.63,1:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEN}From ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.43,1:19:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我能在 iPhone上播放吗\N{\rEN}Can I play this on my iPhone?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.18,1:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这写的是什么\N{\rEN}What is it written?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.34,1:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,范·莫里森\N{\rEN}Van Morrison.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.81,1:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Spotify上有吗\N{\rEN}Is this on Spotify?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.98,1:19:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不懂\N{\rEN}Uncle doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.70,1:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\rEN}Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.53,1:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.57,1:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的那家店\N{\rEN}That shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.74,1:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是一家商店\N{\rEN}It's not a shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.97,1:22:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这个\N{\rEN}Ah, that!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.60,1:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这个吗  我的相机已经很旧了\N{\rEN}You mean this? My camera is quite old.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.56,1:22:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEN}Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.40,1:22:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\rEN}How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.94,1:22:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗\N{\rEN}You do not remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.44,1:22:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是你送我的 叔叔\N{\rEN}You gave it to me, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.57,1:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊 是啊  - 说谎\N{\rEN}- Oh yes. - Lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.07,1:22:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了 对吧\N{\rEN}You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.80,1:22:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这棵树是你的朋友吗\N{\rEN}Is the tree your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.80,1:23:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友吗\N{\rEN}Friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.64,1:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是吗\N{\rEN}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.06,1:23:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你说得对\N{\rEN}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.19,1:23:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的树...朋友\N{\rEN}This is my friend.. Tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.75,1:24:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\rEN}Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.84,1:24:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以借这本书吗\N{\rEN}can i borrow this book
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.51,1:24:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本\N{\rEN}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.01,1:25:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十一篇短篇小说\N{\rEN}"Eleven Short Stories."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.17,1:25:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEN}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.06,1:25:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,波兰龟那篇里的男孩 维克多…\N{\rEN}This boy, Victor, from the tale "The Polam Turtle"...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.93,1:25:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他就跟我一样\N{\rEN}He's like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.77,1:25:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解他正在经历什么\N{\rEN}I understand what he is going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.16,1:25:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你吗\N{\rEN}can i help
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.89,1:25:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.41,1:26:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 你为什么跟妈妈合不来啊\N{\rEN}Uncle, why don't you and mother get along?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.21,1:26:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她这么说的吗\N{\rEN}He told you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.29,1:26:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我谈到你...\N{\rEN}Every time I talk about you...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.29,1:26:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她都会转移话题\N{\rEN}...he changed the topic.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.22,1:26:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\rEN}So.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.85,1:26:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你和妈妈吵架了吗\N{\rEN}Did you quarrel with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.10,1:26:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\rEN}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.06,1:26:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是离家出走吗\N{\rEN}Do you always run away from home?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.48,1:26:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第一次\N{\rEN}This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.82,1:26:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直计划着跟叔叔一起生活\N{\rEN}It was always my plan to stay with Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.74,1:26:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 这算什么\N{\rEN}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.56,1:27:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我是去那边吗\N{\rEN}Thank You. Am I coming here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.52,1:27:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 十分钟后见  - 这也太短了\N{\rEN}- See you in 10 minutes. - That's too short.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.32,1:27:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那就二十分钟\N{\rEN}Then 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.04,1:27:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我明白\N{\rEN}Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.83,1:27:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 知道\N{\rEN}Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.13,1:27:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗\N{\rEN}Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.22,1:27:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去吃午饭吧  - 太好了\N{\rEN}- Then we'll have lunch.  -  Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.09,1:27:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 毛巾放这里  - 谢谢\N{\rEN}- Put the towel here. - Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.61,1:28:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你和妈妈一点都不像\N{\rEN}Uncle and mother are nothing alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.90,1:28:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你指的是哪方面\N{\rEN}You mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.46,1:28:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我们是不同世界的人\N{\rEN}He said Uncle and we live in different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.50,1:28:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是真的吧\N{\rEN}That's probably true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.46,1:28:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rEN}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.84,1:28:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界就是这样形形色色\N{\rEN}This world consists of many different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.55,1:28:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,相关联的 不相关的\N{\rEN}Some are related and some are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.48,1:28:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界...\N{\rEN}My world...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.39,1:28:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你母亲的世界非常不同\N{\rEN}...and your mother's world is very different.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.49,1:28:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那我呢\N{\rEN}What about my world?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.44,1:28:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我身处哪个世界呢\N{\rEN}Where in the world am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.33,1:29:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这条河会流入大海吗\N{\rEN}This river flows into the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.92,1:29:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Yes, to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.51,1:29:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去那里吗\N{\rEN}Are you going there?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.72,1:29:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,下次吧\N{\rEN}Next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.43,1:29:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\rEN}When is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.64,1:29:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就是下次\N{\rEN}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.85,1:29:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,具体呢\N{\rEN}When exactly?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.65,1:29:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就是下次\N{\rEN}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.48,1:29:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就是现在\N{\rEN}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.90,1:29:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\rEN}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.57,1:29:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\rEN}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.59,1:29:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\rEN}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.00,1:29:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\rEN}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.43,1:29:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\rEN}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.64,1:29:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\rEN}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.72,1:30:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐\N{\rEN}Sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.23,1:30:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见\N{\rEN}Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.27,1:30:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你就住在这里吗\N{\rEN}So you live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.61,1:30:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有恶意 Niko 拿上你的东西\N{\rEN}I don't mean anything bad. Niko, get your things.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.07,1:30:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不要  - 我不是在跟你商量\N{\rEN}- Don't want to!  - That's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.32,1:30:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\rEN}Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.99,1:30:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\rEN}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.57,1:31:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\rEN}Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.79,1:31:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意 你随时都可以来\N{\rEN}Come visit whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.96,1:31:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的书我还没读完呢\N{\rEN}I haven't even finished reading your book.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.63,1:31:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,带着吧\N{\rEN}Just bring it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.43,1:31:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会像维克多一样\N{\rEN}I will be like Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.47,1:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\rEN}Won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.15,1:31:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么说  - Niko\N{\rEN}- Do not say like that.   - Niko!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.75,1:31:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了\N{\rEN}Here's to your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.80,1:31:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是你最喜欢的巧克力\N{\rEN}Your favorite chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.48,1:32:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好孩子\N{\rEN}He is a good child.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.98,1:32:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不敢说\N{\rEN}I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.23,1:32:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的父亲...\N{\rEN}Our father...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.36,1:32:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经什么都不认识了\N{\rEN}...he doesn't recognize anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.49,1:32:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去疗养院探望他吗\N{\rEN}Are you going to visit him at the nursing home?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.82,1:32:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他再也不会和以前一样了\N{\rEN}He will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.76,1:32:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的在清扫厕所吗\N{\rEN}Is it true that you work cleaning toilets?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.70,1:33:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\rEN}Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.45,1:33:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.24,1:35:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是高志\N{\rEN}Hello, this is Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.99,1:35:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高志 你好\N{\rEN}This is Takashi, hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.07,1:35:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了\N{\rEN}I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.21,1:35:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 您对我很好 对此 我真的非常感激\N{\rEN}Mr. Hiyarama, you have been kind to me. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.67,1:36:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,满分十分可以打九分\N{\rEN}The rating is 9 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.04,1:36:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我很难当面跟你讲 我辞职了\N{\rEN}That's why it's hard for me to say this, but I resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.05,1:36:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.34,1:36:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,钱我会马上还你的\N{\rEN}I will immediately reimburse you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.34,1:36:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 那谁来替你\N{\rEN}Wait, what about your sif?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.78,1:36:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.53,1:36:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们短期内找不到替代者\N{\rEN}We can't find a replacement anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.07,1:36:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我应该怎么办\N{\rEN}No replacement? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.25,1:36:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那你今天就只能加班了\N{\rEN}You have to fill the shift today.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.75,1:36:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我会很快的\N{\rEN}what can Sorry, I'll be brief.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.33,1:36:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEN}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.80,1:36:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.38,1:36:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是新来的吗  - 我马上结束了\N{\rEN}- Are you new?   - I'm about to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.33,1:37:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEN}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.83,1:37:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他人呢\N{\rEN}Where's Takashi?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.00,1:38:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经打过三遍电话了 为什么没人接\N{\rEN}I've called three times. Why isn't anyone picking up?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.43,1:38:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能顶一天\N{\rEN}I'm just doing it for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.89,1:38:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧找个新人\N{\rEN}Find someone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.96,1:40:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是佐藤 是被派到这里的...\N{\rEN}I'm Sato. I was told to come here immediately...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.96,1:40:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...来顶替之前的人的班次\N{\rEN}...and took over the shift from the previous employee.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.51,1:40:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是从那里开始吗\N{\rEN}Should I start there?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.88,1:40:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.86,1:43:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\rEN}- Hello - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.80,1:44:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得这之前是什么吗\N{\rEN}Do you remember what this used to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.68,1:44:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经老了\N{\rEN}That means we are old.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.17,1:45:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里夏·海史密斯【美国女作家】对焦虑了如指掌\N{\rEN}Patricia Highsmith knows all about anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.02,1:45:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉读者恐惧和焦虑完全是不同的东西\N{\rEN}He showed me that fear and anxiety are different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.72,1:46:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人是怎么回事\N{\rEN}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.81,1:46:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就是..\N{\rEN}You know..
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.69,1:46:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我能进来吗\N{\rEN}can i come in
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.24,1:46:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rEN}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.19,1:46:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟香烟一起打包好了\N{\rEN}Packed cigarettes and plastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.02,1:48:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以来一只吗\N{\rEN}Can I have one?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.02,1:48:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很久没有抽烟了\N{\rEN}I haven't smoked for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.49,1:49:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的那个人是你吗\N{\rEN}Did you see us at the bar earlier?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.50,1:49:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你是个常客\N{\rEN}It seems like you always go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.26,1:49:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.17,1:49:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,从开业至今已有五六年了\N{\rEN}It's been five or six years since the place opened.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.35,1:49:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样\N{\rEN}So it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.10,1:49:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个很好的地方\N{\rEN}It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.40,1:49:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她的前夫\N{\rEN}I'm her ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.08,1:49:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEN}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.45,1:49:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离婚已经快七年了\N{\rEN}It's been about seven years since we divorced.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.34,1:49:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经再婚了\N{\rEN}I've remarried.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.59,1:50:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,距离上次见他已经七年了\N{\rEN}It's been seven years since I last saw him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.93,1:50:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我得了癌症\N{\rEN}I have cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.86,1:50:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,癌细胞一直在扩散\N{\rEN}The cancer has spread.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.86,1:50:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身体因为化疗十分不堪\N{\rEN}My body was swollen from chemotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.54,1:50:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我...\N{\rEN}Then I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.08,1:50:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,……突然觉得自己欠她一个道歉\N{\rEN}...suddenly felt that I owed him an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.17,1:50:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我挺过去了\N{\rEN}Nothing bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.63,1:50:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是道歉\N{\rEN}Maybe not an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.00,1:50:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要感谢她\N{\rEN}I want to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.35,1:50:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能也不是\N{\rEN}No, it's not about that either.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.43,1:50:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想见见她 仅此而已\N{\rEN}I just want to see him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.95,1:51:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来一瓶吗\N{\rEN}Do you want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.74,1:51:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩一瓶\N{\rEN}I still have one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.46,1:51:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗...\N{\rEN}In that case,...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.25,1:51:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEN}...I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.82,1:51:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请照顾好她\N{\rEN}Please take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.95,1:51:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我们不是那种关系  - 拜托你了\N{\rEN}- No, we don't have that kind of relationship.  - I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.78,1:51:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一个食客\N{\rEN}We don't have a relationship like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.55,1:52:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那些阴影..\N{\rEN}Shadow..
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.89,1:52:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被覆盖之后会变得更黑吗\N{\rEN}Do they get darker when overwritten?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.65,1:52:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你\N{\rEN}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.77,1:52:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有那么多不理解的事情呢\N{\rEN}There are so many things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.10,1:52:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,生命就这样结束了\N{\rEN}That's how life ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.28,1:52:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真不甘心啊\N{\rEN}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.29,1:52:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在就去验证一下吧\N{\rEN}Let's find out now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.30,1:52:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.19,1:53:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,站在那\N{\rEN}Stand there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.02,1:53:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.24,1:53:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么\N{\rEN}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.33,1:53:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来一样啊\N{\rEN}Looks the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.41,1:53:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是更黑了吗\N{\rEN}Isn't it darker?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.29,1:53:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吧\N{\rEN}Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.17,1:53:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说这看起来更黑了\N{\rEN}That looks darker to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.42,1:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是看不出有什么区别\N{\rEN}I don't see the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.13,1:53:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 看\N{\rEN}Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.27,1:53:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色要深一点才有意义\N{\rEN}The shade needs to be darker to make sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.60,1:53:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太执着了\N{\rEN}You're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.56,1:53:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没什么变化\N{\rEN}Still no changes?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.11,1:53:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\rEN}Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.70,1:53:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEN}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.17,1:54:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,玩儿追影子吗\N{\rEN}Want to play with shadows?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.34,1:54:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我来追\N{\rEN}I'm the one chasing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.81,1:54:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\rEN}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.89,1:54:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开始了\N{\rEN}I start.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.27,1:54:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跑吧\N{\rEN}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.11,1:54:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗  - 太难了\N{\rEN}- Are you okay? -  This is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.19,1:54:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在换我\N{\rEN}Now I'm the one chasing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.44,1:54:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定吗 准备好了吗  - 我要开始了\N{\rEN}- Are you sure? Ready?  - I start.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.41,1:54:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得手了\N{\rEN}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.71,1:54:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太难了\N{\rEN}Very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.21,1:54:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很累人啊 踩到了\N{\rEN}This is tiring. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.67,1:54:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很接近了 我踩到你了  - 真的吗\N{\rEN}- That's close. I stepped on you.   - Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.03,2:00:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译：霓虹狮子_

